<div class="definition" id="definition-OSV" acro="OSV" titletext="Orthogonal Set of Vectors">
<h5 class="definition">
<span class="type">Definition </span><span class="acro">OSV</span> <span class="titletext"> Orthogonal Set of Vectors</span>
</h5>
<p>Suppose that $S=\set{\vectorlist{u}{n}}$ is a set of vectors from $\complex{m}$.  Then $S$ is an <em class="term">orthogonal set</em> if every pair of different vectors from $S$ is orthogonal, that is $\innerproduct{\vect{u}_i}{\vect{u}_j}=0$ whenever $i\neq j$.</p>
